<HL>
   Business Brief -- PepsiCo Inc.:
   Pizza Hut Franchisee Plans
   Soft-Drink Shift to Coke
</HL>
<DATE>
10/09/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   KO PEP
</CO>
